title: [Tricky Treats]
description: Bits of dried seaweed, black coral, and mollusk are still stuck to the walls, and a long counter made from various pieces of driftwood divides the room.  Shelving along the walls holds a variety of foodstuffs, while behind the counter is cooking space.  Tables, ovens, and stoves are staged behind the counter for the preperation of the wares.
